  m_Name: MilitaryRecord_08
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 40
  title: "B\xE1o c\xE1o qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i #8 \u2014 B\xE1o c\xE1o th\u01B0\u01A1ng
    vong"
  category: 5
  content: "\u0110\u1EA1i t\xE1 Morrison \u2014 b\xE1o c\xE1o th\u01B0\u01A1ng vong
    cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng. T\xEDnh \u0111\u1EBFn 04:00 ng\xE0y 14/10: Thi\u1EBFu t\xE1
    Chen \u2014 KIA. Trung \xFAy Park \u2014 KIA. Trung s\u0129 Lopez \u2014 MIA
    (b\u1ECB c\u1EAFn, t\u1EF1 c\xE1ch ly). H\u01A1n 200 l\xEDnh th\u01B0\u01A1ng
    vong. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i m\u1EA5t ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t ho\xE0n to\xE0n khu d\xE2n c\u01B0
    v\xE0 chung c\u01B0. L\u1EC7nh cu\u1ED1i: to\xE0n qu\xE2n r\xFAt v\u1EC1 c\u0103n
    c\u1EE9 ph\xEDa nam, \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i v\u0169 kh\xED v\xE0 h\u1ED3 s\u01A1.
    N\u1EBFu ai c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng \u0111\u1ECDc \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c: l\u1EA5y b\u1ED9
    k\xEDch n\u1ED5 \u1EDF t\xF2a cao t\u1EA7ng g\u1EA7n c\u1EA7u, k\xEDch ho\u1EA1t
    qu\u1EA3 bom \u1EDF tr\u1EA1m ph\xE1t s\xF3ng. \u0110\xE2y l\xE0 l\u1EC7nh cu\u1ED1i
    c\xF9ng c\u1EE7a t\xF4i."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
